.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-LISTFORWARDS-FEE-MIN" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-listforwards-fee-min \- FEAT-2501 minimum single forward fee_msat among settled forwards
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-listforwards-fee-min
.SH DESCRIPTION
node-listforwards-fee-min for lightning CLI (FEAT-2501).
.PP
Returns the minimum fee_msat value among all settled forwards recorded by the node.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
